  "title": "Admin cum Account Executive [WCNH]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Administration & Office Support</strong></p><ul><li><p>Oversaw and coordinated <strong>daily office operations</strong> to ensure smooth workflow.</p></li><li><p>Managed <strong>local minor purchases</strong>, scheduled tasks, and coordinated jobs efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Prepared <strong>quotations</strong> and followed up with clients or vendors.</p></li><li><p>Handled <strong>staff attendance, timesheets, overtime, and expense claims</strong> accurately and on schedule.</p></li><li><p>Supported <strong>HR administration</strong>, including onboarding documents, leave tracking, and personnel records.</p></li><li><p>Coordinated <strong>meetings, travel arrangements, and company events</strong> as required.</p></li><li><p>Maintained an <strong>organized filing system</strong> (hardcopy and digital) for easy reference and audit readiness.</p></li><li><p>Communicated with <strong>vendors, service providers, and customers</strong>, ensuring timely follow-up and support.</p></li><li><p>Prepared and printed <strong>reports</strong> as needed.</p></li><li><p>Performed other <strong>ad-hoc duties</strong> assigned by management.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Accounting & Finance Support</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepared and processed <strong>sales orders, invoices, and delivery orders</strong> with accuracy.</p></li><li><p>Conducted <strong>monthly reconciliations</strong> for <strong>banks, suppliers, and customer accounts</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Maintained <strong>accurate GST records</strong> and assisted with timely submission.</p></li><li><p>Prepared and issued <strong>Statements of Account (SOA)</strong> for customer payment follow-ups.</p></li><li><p>Updated <strong>inventory and sales order reports</strong> to reflect real-time data.</p></li><li><p><strong>Verified bank transactions against company records</strong> to ensure all cash movements are accounted for.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p></li></ul>",
